            <title>[LUCENE-2274] Catch exceptions in Threads created by JUnit tasks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2274</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;On hudson we had several assertions failed in TestRAMDirectory, that were never caught by the error reportier in JUnit (as the test itsself did not fail). This patch adds a handler for uncaught exceptions to LuceneTestCase(J4) that let the test fail in tearDown().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
